Our Services

Our Cleaning Angels will have a detailed work order of your reservation for each of the services we offer at CLEANING WITH LOVE, we recommend selecting additional services for all first time or one time reservations.
Our Services
How to Get Started
You Only Need
1 • Select the service you need.
Specify all the details and extra requirements if applicable
2 • Select the time and day that works best for you.
If the date you select is not available, we will send you a message and we will do our best to accommodate around your availability
3 • It will be a professional service in the shortest possible time.
The duration is between 1.5 - 3 hours
4 • Satisfaction.
Of having the best and most experienced team working for you.
Why Us

• WE ARE BONDED AND INSURED
  • 100% SATIFACTION GUARANTEE
  • ALL CLEANING SUPPLIES INCLUDED
  • EASY ON LINE BOOKING ( TAKES ONLY 60 SECONDS )
  • CERTIFIED PROFFESIONAL CLEANERS

• We treat your things with the same care and attention as a priceless treasure, because we understand the importance your belongings have to you.
  • For our clients only the best is acceptable. That is why we use the best products and equipment. We use vacuum cleaners with a triple Hepa filter system, and an Allergen Sealing system that traps the dust and any allegens inside the vacuum cleaner and reducing the number of contaminants in the room. All our products are also hypoallergenic, and eco friendly.

When working with Cleaning with Love, you find yourself in the lucky position of having partnered with a brand whose signature is Excellence. Kathy is a true business mind who is passionate about what she does. My home is transformed after her visits through the highest quality of work.
EMILY PERO
Senior Product Designer

We hired Service with Love to organize our closets in our apartment and our house. Kathy is a true professional, in every sense of the word. She has a calm demeanor that is easy to be around and is a wonderful human being which made the experience of working with her even better. Kathy is very thorough in her process, from packing to moving, unboxing everything and knowing just how to arrange it.
 We left Kathy alone for several days in our house and when we returned our closets looked like a boutique. My husband was so elated that he asked if she could live with us! Kathy’s knowledge and skill goes farther than you could predict. She went above and beyond to ameliorate any issues with space and spared no attention to detail. Kathy will arrive without any judgment, help you make decisions if you are having difficulty and is objective in an almost therapeutic way. Thanks to Kathy and Service with Love our home is a sanctuary and we have continued to use them weekly.
MRS REBECCA VANYO AND BRUCE VANYO
Senior Product Designer

Kathy has been working for my family for over 3 years. In many ways, she runs my household. She has completely reorganized every square inch of of my apartment. She has come up with methods to organize things not only efficiently, but beautifully. Kathy is a joy and pleasure to be around, always working with a smile on her face. My home would be an absolute mess without her.  Recently, we moved from our apartment that we had lived in for the past six years into a new place and Kathy ensured that the entire process was seamless helping to both pack and unpack. She organized my entire new apartment in two days time. She is not only an angel, but also incredibly talented.
MRS JORDEN BICKHAN
Senior Product Designer

Terms and Conditions
Arrival windows:

• In consideration of traffic, weather conditions, customers adding services, and blockages, please allow a window of at least 2 hours from your scheduled appointment time. For your convenience: if you cannot be at home, it is easier to provide a password or access to the entry code.
Payment:

• We accept Visa / Master Card Debit and Credit cards for all one time and reoccurring service.
  • A verification charge may appear at the time of scheduling your service. Payment is charged in full upon the completion of the service.
  • A $25 fee is charged for all NSF or declined transactions
Circumstantial Rates:

• Last minute Cancellation / Lock Out / Rescheduling Fee: If you require a cancellation, rescheduling of your service, we kindly ask you contact us by e-mail at customerservice@servicewithlove.org, by 12:00 p.m., 2 business days before your booking (holidays and weekends are not business days).
    Example: If your service is scheduled for Tuesday, you must e-mail us by 12:00 p.m. the previous Friday. (Voicemails and calls to cancel services are not accepted unless you receive a confirmation e-mail from us.) Any schedule changes within 2 business days prior to the appointment are billed up to 50% fee of the service fee in respecting our meticulous scheduling efforts, reserving a crew of workers for you, paying them for their booked time regardless. A client not home when we arrive is considered a cancellation/lockout, unless previous arrangements have been made to provide access to the property, and they have been confirmed by us prior to our arrival.
  • Waiting Time Fee: Should the client need the cleaning team to wait within the agreed arrival window, there is a waiting charge of $40 per hour per Cleaning Angel.
  • Unsafe Conditions Fee: Our team reserves the right to refuse service to any client whose worksite poses an undue health or safety hazard. At the point of refusal, for this reason, 50% of the total of the estimate becomes payable as compensation for negligence.
  •
Scope of work:

• Furniture Lifting/Moving: If you require us to clean behind a fridge, shelf, or furniture, please pull it out for us in advance. We do not move anything over 20 lbs. We are not a moving or handyman service. We also do not wish to scratch furniture, flooring and we take care to prevent injury of our Cleaning Angels.  
  • Wall and Floor Washing: Entire washing of walls/floors by hand is beyond our regular scope of vacuuming and light-duty mopping. By booking our service, you agree to floors mopped with commercial “microfibre flat mops.” Such mopping will satisfy 97% of flooring needs. We do not clean grout in between tiled floors or walls (except in showers). Other companies provide specialized “grout steam cleaning” service.

We reserve the right to reject your order when there is :

Dishonesty… if we deem the level of labor is beyond the Work Order, you confirmed during booking. (example: you said 2 bed 2 baths, but upon arrival, it is 4 bed 4 baths!)

Safety Hazard… your property has any of the above items that are part of our “Out of Scope” list.

Unreasonable Cleaning Conditions… your property has obviously not been maintained, has been abused for years as in this sample photo

Abuse… the client or representative of the client verbally abuses our staff.

Harassment… the client or representative of the client harasses our staff with eg. lewd actions, or by following, watching behind their back, micromanaging their work, etc. Such behavior stresses people out and guarantees low service performance and results.

Elevator Down/No Elevator… your condo high rise elevators are shut down, or none exist. We cannot carry our equipment up and down more than 4 levels of stairs.
IMPORT INFORMATION
We hate to find ourselves in such unpleasant circumstances for both parties, but upon a rejection of service, we do charge 100% of the service fee.

1. Customer satisfaction policy :
  • To ensure your satisfaction with our service upon arrival, we require clients to do a free Walk Through going over your Work Order.
  • For liability protection, we hold the right to take before and after photos.
  • Upon completion, we require clients to complete a free Peace of Mind Walk Through and sign off upon satisfaction.

Due to the subjective nature of the cleaning industry, we do not offer refunds.

  1. Complaint Validity Period :
  • All cleaning is final 24 hours after completion. Clients are required to give another team a chance to fix all complaints resulting from the Work Order and scope before reviews are posted to public media.
  • Cleaning With Love reserves the right to repair any damage that may arise as a result of the cleaning by any means and the client who, by accepting the service, explicitly declares that the company can take whatever steps it deems appropriate to repair the damage.
  • If the customer or their representatives refuse to consent to the steps necessary to repair the damage, the company will only provide a monetary sum that does not exceed what it would have cost the company to perform them. The company will not be responsible for any expenses past this.
  1. Non-Solicitation of Staff :
  • As a client, you agree not to hire any present or past staff of Cleaning With Love for any home-related service outside of your service purchases with Cleaning With Love. If you hire our cleaning staff to work privately, you must pay $3000 to our company.
  1. Confidentiality and security :  
  • As our client, we respect your privacy and dignity. We keep your information confidential and keys/passcodes securely stored. Also, all documents, personnel information, communication (verbal / written / media) etc. are owned by Cleaning With Love . Do not disclose to the public outside of your service.
IMPORT INFORMATION
We hate to find ourselves in such unpleasant circumstances for both parties, but upon a rejection of service, we do charge 100% of the service fee.
As a valued customer, we thank you in advance for your understanding and adherence to these Terms and Conditions.

fields.title:
Regular
Cleaning
fields.description:
If you dream of having a totally impeccable home without spending the time or effort, we at CLEANING WITH LOVE are ready to help you. With our regular cleaning service, we offer you a great cleaning job at an affordable price. Our Cleaning Angels are true professionals who will carefully review the space and immediately develop a strategy to carry out the work, making sure that at the end of the day your property will fulfill all your espectations.

Our standard cleaning includes dusting and washing all accessible surfaces, cleaning the exterior of kitchen appliances and cabinets, basic bathroom cleaning, vacuuming, and mopping all floors. At CLEANING WITH LOVE, we provide all our cleaning supplies at no additional cost.

fields.title:
Deep
Cleaning
fields.description:
Sometimes, even when using a cleaning service on a regular basis, certain areas can get neglected. With the deep cleaning offered at CLEANING WITH LOVE, we pay more attention to details often overlooked, and with our expert Cleaning Angels, we will prepare your home for easier and faster cleanings in the future.

Deep cleaning includes all the services of a standard cleaning, but with more attention to areas that you, or other services, may have forgotten to clean over time. We also include refrigerator and oven cleaning. Our cleaning will make your home look more sparkling than ever.

This type of cleaning is often recommended for the first visit. This will allow you to schedule our standard service on your next visit, which will be more than enough to keep your home in tip-top shape.

fields.title:
Green
Cleaning
fields.description: It is important to CLEANING WITH LOVE to support your ecologically friendly lifestyle. To do so, we use safe, effective, non-toxic, biodegradable, and nature-derived products. It is by using these products, along with low-impact processes, we make your home or office shine and you to achieve simpler and more ecologically friendly lifestyles. We have equipment that performs a 100% ecologically friendly cleaning. Just ask, and we’ll assign a green cleaning crew at no additional charge. Our Cleaning Angels will take your special requests, and if you want your cleaning to be done with your preferred cleaning products, we at CLEANING WITH LOVE are ready to meet your requirements.

fields.title:
Move In / Out
Cleaning
fields.description:
If you are moving to a new location, please consider our moving cleaning service as a part of your plans. When you vacate your property, a professional cleaning will have you leaving the space ready to prepare for the new occupant. Similarly, when you are arriving in a new property an cleaning angel will take care of the mess that often results from a move.

At Cleaning With Love we focus on the details to make sure that your old or new space is sparkling clean and ready for its new journey. Our specialized moving services include everything in our Regular Cleaning service, but with additional focus on the areas needed to get your space just the way you want it. Our team of Cleaning Angels will clean and sanitize from top to bottom, resulting in a warm, stress-free welcome to your new home.

fields.title:
Office
Cleaning
fields.description:
If you want to arrive at an impeccable workplace, CLEANING WITH LOVE is ready to help you.

Whether you run a small business or are part of a large company, making sure your offices are kept clean and orderly helps create an efficient work environment as well as positive first impressions for your clients. With our office cleaning service, CLEANING WITH LOVE offers you excellent office cleaning at an affordable price.

Each office cleaning includes common work areas and bathrooms. We also bring all the cleaning supplies at no additional cost.

All of our Cleaning Angels are carefully selected by us so that we can offer you the highest quality cleaning. We are insured and bonded to ensure the security of your office. Each job is thoroughly inspected, so you know that you are getting the best cleaning possible with each visit.

fields.title:
AIRBNB
Cleaning
fields.description:
If your wish is for your guests to enter an impeccable home without having to invest time and effort yourself, CLEANING WITH LOVE offers an excellent cleaning service at an affordable price. The cleanliness of the space is often the most crucial factor in your guest’s review.

Our dedicated Cleaning Angels are true professionals and make sure your home is transformed into a spotless place for your rental guests. We will review your space and quickly detect the needs of the site to make it look its best.

Your wish is our Cleaning Angels command. Maintain your 5-star Airbnb rating with a professional cleaning. Do you want a well-made bed for your guests? Folded towels? We’ll send out trained and trusted Cleaning Angels who are experienced in taking care of every detail, making a unique space for our clients.

fields.title:
Laundry
Service
fields.description:
The laundry service is washing, drying, folding, and putting away your clothes during your scheduled home cleaning. There is no need to waste time doing laundry yourself! Our Cleaning Angels are also experts in laundry services.

Each client’s clothing is cared for separately and diligently by our Cleaning Angels, who care about preserving the quality of each item’s fabrics.

Please note that laundry is only offered as an additional service in conjunction with your scheduled home cleaning. We do not provide laundry services on their own. There must be a laundry room in the building or a washer and dryer in your home to use this service.

The customer must provide detergent and fabric softener. Please also note that we do NOT iron your clothes.

Our team of Organizing Angels works hand in hand with our clients, guiding them on the path of organization, teaching them the gifts of maximizing space, minimizing clutter and maintaining organization, bringing comfort and harmony, and leaving behind the chaos that brings the mess.

fields.title: How Do We Work
fields.items: Our decorating professionals can make basic thru comprehensive improvements, distributing, furnishing, and decorating your space. As our client, you won’t have to lift a finger. We carry out the direction, execution, and management of the entire project, from placing a plant in a strategic place to selecting the colors of the walls and all the necessary details needed to give an incredible look to your home or office. Our experts will coordinate with stores, manufacturers, suppliers, installers, and we help with everything you need to achieve the perfect balance. Our service is ideal if you have a space that is in good condition, and you only need to give it your personal style using elements such as lighting, color, materials, furniture, and decoration. The process begins by identifying the design parameters, needs, and expectations of you, our client, and completes with the satisfaction of seeing your spaces, just as you imagined them.

fields.title: What is the First Step
fields.items:
The first step is an introductory visit where we take photographs and measurements of the space.

We make sure to take note of any unique features, and then carry out a creative workshop with you to build a mood board with phrases and personal tastes that allow us to understand your style.

From that mood board, we start the design process and then meet again with you to go over the designs and make any necessary adjustments.

Once refined and approved, our decorating professionals begin the process of executing your design.

fields.title: What are you looking for in your space?
fields.items:
We focus on bringing out the great potential of your space by creating a design that fits your home, is functional, and that generates its own identity.

Our creation process goes hand in hand with how you see your environment and what you want from it, so it is crucial that you allow us to learn about all that you imagine and the desires in your heart so that we can design the home of your dreams.

fields.title: What spaces we work?
fields.items:
Nurseries
Bedrooms
Dining rooms
Living rooms
Bathrooms
Kitchens
Basements
Interior and exterior gardens
Home offices
Closets

fields.title: What does our work include?
fields.items:
Look & Feel
In the search for your individual style, we perform an interview to learn about your tastes and way of life. Incorporating this information, we choose a palette of colors, materials, and references.

3D modeling
A model of the space to be decorated will be created. This allows you to have a better visualization of the design elements and how they function in your space. This process is key to understanding the dimensions of the place and will help refine the design.

High-quality renderings
You will receive renders with the final version of your design. These images will let you have a better idea of ​​how it will look and will reflect the final result.

fields.title: What is our cost?
fields.items: Our professional decorators want to give you the satisfaction of seeing your space, just as you imagined it. That is why we have created several plans to fit the needs of your space. Remember that these prices may vary based on your unique needs, as no two spaces, like their owners, are the same. We also offer completely custom solutions for your decorating needs if you don’t see something that fits your specific space.
